metadata.name: It Sounds Fantastic, But... #1/150
metadata.description:
Digital post-collage work based on a 1903 photograph of actress Anna Stanton, found on the Wikimedia Commons.

Words cut out from 1950s sci-fi digests and 1970s magazines.

For more, look for 5000 Space Aliens art on KnownOrigin, Foundation, Objkt, and Opensea!

3000 x 3000 pixels
